title: Sawbones: Sneezing
description:
Welcome to all the owners of human bodies! You're gonna love these things, they can run, jump ... and every once in a while they uncontrollably blast snot out of your face at 100 MPH. This week on Sawbones: Sneezing.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
